29:06.872 --> 29:13.842
It allows you to see light and light.

29:14.306 --> 29:20.335
Light allows us to see Jesus at work in the midst of all of the things that are going on in our lives.

29:20.716 --> 29:25.202
Light allows us to survive the dark winters of our lives.

29:25.603 --> 29:41.106
Light shows us some things that we don't want to see, and light shows us some things that we don't want to know, but yet their scripture reminds us, do not be afraid!

29:50.274 --> 29:52.056
The person who should have been most afraid.

29:52.116 --> 30:07.035
She puts praising God, praising God for the new baby, praising God for this disruption in her life, praising God for the light of the world.

30:12.202 --> 30:13.183
What have you been doing?

30:18.049 --> 30:18.930
Seek the light.

30:21.058 --> 30:22.279
How do you seek the light?

30:24.342 --> 30:25.163
Praise the Lord.

30:27.786 --> 30:29.868
Praise the Lord in expectation.

30:30.789 --> 30:32.651
Praise the Lord in advance.

30:33.152 --> 30:43.203
Praise the Lord knowing that you know, that you know, that you know, that you know, that you know, that you know, that you know, that your praise of God leads to light.

30:43.223 --> 30:45.586
And light turns the world right side up.

30:49.474 --> 30:50.876
The songwriter put it like this.

30:53.138 --> 30:54.339
He said, light of the world.

30:56.322 --> 30:58.084
You step down into darkness.

31:00.306 --> 31:03.630
Open our eyes and let us see.

31:05.252 --> 31:09.637
Beauty that made this heart adore you.

31:09.677 --> 31:10.618
Come on, Mr. Nard.

31:11.218 --> 31:14.482
Hope of a life spent with you.

31:14.946 --> 31:27.780
And the next verse that a lot of us don't know says, says, King of all days, oh, so highly exalted, glorious in heaven above.

31:28.381 --> 31:36.710
Unbelievable, you came to the earth, you created all for love's sake, ha ha, became poor.

31:36.730 --> 31:39.913
And then it says, I know you know it, I know you know it.

31:40.273 --> 31:41.174
Come on, Mr. Nark.

31:41.535 --> 31:44.498
It says, here I am to worship.

31:44.834 --> 31:45.195
Right?

31:46.339 --> 31:49.388
Here I am to bow down.

31:49.649 --> 31:50.571
Come on y'all help me.

31:51.354 --> 31:59.378
Here I am.

33:14.210 --> 33:28.672
to see some more life, to see the King of Kings and the Lord of Lords, to see the mighty good shepherd, the merciful God, to see that God is still God.

33:29.593 --> 33:31.135
That's what Christmas is about.

33:32.457 --> 33:34.420
It's not about all the stuff.

33:36.023 --> 33:38.226
It's not even about Santa Claus.

33:38.882 --> 33:51.080
But it is indeed about the light of the world, opening our eyes so that we might be reminded that there is indeed what?

33:51.781 --> 33:53.063
Yes.

33:54.245 --> 33:55.247
Jesus is born.

33:56.268 --> 33:57.730
That's the best news I've ever heard.

33:57.790 --> 33:58.732
How about you?

33:59.193 --> 34:00.815
Jesus is born.

34:00.835 --> 34:07.525
The light has come.

34:07.545 --> 34:08.146
Nothing will ever be the same.

34:09.314 --> 34:09.796
Rejoice!

34:10.580 --> 34:15.360
Rejoice!

34:15.380 --> 34:15.762
Amen.

